    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stock comprising pieces of material that are small or otherwise of non-standard dimensions. As applied to timber, usually denotes the sectional dimensions (thickness and breadth) in contradistinction to the length, of a square-edged piece of nonstandard dimensions. For a block of stone, a piece measured in all three dimensions.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
